title: Cops: SUV, tractor trailer crash on Montauk Hwy. in Moriches
text:
Cops: SUV, tractor trailer crash on Montauk Hwy. in Moriches Updated February 23, 2017 6:51 AM By William Murphy 
advertisement | advertise on newsday Suffolk County police and firefighters investigate an accident involving a sport utility vehicle and a tractor trailer on Montuak Highway near Barnes Road on Thursday, Feb. 23, 2017. (Credit: John Walthers) 
A sport utility vehicle crashed into the rear of a tractor trailer parked along the eastbound side of Montauk Highway in Moriches early Thursday, closing all lanes in both directions, Suffolk County police said. 
Photos of the crash show the front seats of the SUV crushed under the body of the trailer, and the front tires of the SUV appeared to be touching the rear tires of the trailer.
